<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-50 via-white to-green-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-lime-500 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
          MORFOLOGIA
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-lime-600">Gli avverbi</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl">
        88
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 font-semibold">
      Gli avverbi danno una sfumatura di significato particolare a un verbo, a un aggettivo o a un altro avverbio. Possono essere:
    </p>

    <ul class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di modo</strong> (come?) → bene, male, volentieri… e gli avverbi che si formano unendo il suffisso <strong>-mente</strong> a un aggettivo (lentamente...)</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di quantità</strong> (quanto?) → molto, poco, troppo, più, meno, assai, abbastanza…</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di luogo</strong> (dove?) → qui, lì, qua, là, giù, lassù, dentro, davanti, sopra…</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-purple-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di tempo</strong> (quando?) → ora, adesso, oggi, ieri, domani, già, spesso, mai, poi, sempre, presto, tardi…</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-pink-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di affermazione</strong> → sì, certo, sicuramente, appunto, davvero...</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di negazione</strong> → no, non, neppure, mica…</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>di dubbio</strong> → forse, probabilmente, eventualmente, magari, circa…</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold mr-2">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      Sottolinea gli avverbi.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Mi ha salutato <strong>affettuosamente</strong>.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• I ladri scapparono <strong>assai</strong> <strong>lontano</strong>.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Sono venuto <strong>appunto</strong> per questo.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <strong>Certo</strong>, ti aiuto <strong>volentieri</strong>.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <strong>Probabilmente</strong> vinceremo il concorso.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <strong>Spesso</strong> parli <strong>troppo</strong> <strong>forte</strong>.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Vieni <strong>qua</strong> con me.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <strong>Forse</strong> <strong>domani</strong> nevicherà anche <strong>qui</strong>.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Reference -->
  <div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-red-600 font-bold text-base md:text-lg">Esercizi p. 176 e 179</p>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
